"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>formatted fields; properties</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>fields; formatted fields</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>controls; formatted fields</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນກຳນົດຮູບແບບ; ຄຸນສົມບັດ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນ; ຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນກຳນົດຮູບແບບ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຄວບຄຸມ; ຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນກຳນົດຮູບແບບ</bookmark_value>"

#. F35Zg
#: 01170002.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170002.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150774\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Special properties of a formatted field"
msgstr "ຄຸນສົມບັດພິເສດຂອງຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນກຳນົດຮູບແບບ"

#. X63EU
#: 01170002.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170002.xhp\n"
"par_id3156410\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Formatting</emph>: You can set the <emph>Formatting</emph> property by clicking the <emph>...</emph> button in the <emph>Formatting</emph> line of the <emph>Properties: Formatted Field</emph> dialog. The <emph>Number Format</emph> dialog appears."
msgstr "<emph>ການກຳນົດຮູບແບບ</emph>: ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າຮູບແບບໄດ້ໂດຍການຄລິກປຸ່ມ <emph>...</emph> ໃນແຖວ <emph>ການກຳນົດຮູບແບບ</emph>."

#. dUCjf
#: 01170002.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170002.xhp\n"
"par_id3150443\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the formatted field is connected to the text field of a database, the entries in this field will be treated as text. If the formatted field is connected to a field of the database that can be displayed as a number, the input is treated as numbers. The date and time are also handled internally as numbers."
msgstr "ຖ້າຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນກຳນົດຮູບແບບເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນ, ຂໍ້ມູນຈະຖືກປະມວນຜົນຕາມປະເພດຂອງຖານຂໍ້ມູນນັ້ນໆ (ຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ຕົວເລກ)."

#. GFBfu
#: 01170002.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170002.xhp\n"
"par_id3150976\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Min. value</emph> and <emph>Max. value</emph>: You can enter the minimum and maximum numeric value for a formatted field. The min and max values determine the output of existing data (Example: Min. value is <emph>5</emph>, the connected database field contains the integer value <emph>3</emph>. The output is <emph>5</emph>, but the value in the database is not modified) and the input of new data (Example: Max. value is <emph>10</emph> and you enter <emph>20</emph>. The input is corrected and <emph>10</emph> is written in the database). If the fields are not filled in for <emph>Min. value</emph> and <emph>Max. value</emph>, no limits will be applied. For formatted fields that are connected to a database text field, these two values and the <emph>Default value</emph> do not apply."
msgstr "<emph>ຄ່າຕ່ຳສຸດ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ຄ່າສູງສຸດ</emph>: ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດຄ່າຕົວເລກຕ່ຳສຸດ ແລະ ສູງສຸດສຳລັບຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້."

#. RZxmD
#: 01170002.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170002.xhp\n"
"par_id3153665\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Default value</emph>: This value is set for new records as the default value."
msgstr "<emph>ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ</emph>: ຄ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່."

#. GKUnE
#: 01170003.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170003.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Special Tips for Date Fields"
msgstr "ເຄັດລັບພິເສດສຳລັບຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນວັນທີ"

#. UAhW3
#: 01170003.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170003.xhp\n"
"bm_id3150445\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>date fields; properties</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນວັນທີ; ຄຸນສົມບັດ</bookmark_value>"

#. mJFQE
#: 01170003.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170003.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150445\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Special Tips for Date Fields"
msgstr "ເຄັດລັບພິເສດສຳລັບຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນວັນທີ"

#. 9NrxF
#: 01170003.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170003.xhp\n"
"par_id3154230\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you enter a year using two digits, the corresponding four digit value is determined by a setting in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - $[officename] - General</emph>. For example, if <emph>1935</emph> is set as the lower limiting value and you enter <emph>34</emph> as a date value, then the result is <emph>2034</emph> instead of <emph>1934</emph>."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານປ້ອນປີເປັນເລກສອງຫຼັກ, ລະບົບຈະກຳນົດເປັນສີ່ຫຼັກຕາມການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນ <emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ - $[officename] - ທົ່ວໄປ</emph>."

#. FQCuJ
#: 01170003.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170003.xhp\n"
"par_id3149205\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The pre-set limit value will be saved for each document."
msgstr "ຄ່າຈຳກັດທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າຈະຖືກບັນທຶກໄວ້ໃນແຕ່ລະເອກະສານ."

#. F69UY
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Special Tips for Table Controls"
msgstr "ເຄັດລັບພິເສດສຳລັບການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ"

#. 9WeNE
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"bm_id3109850\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>table controls; properties</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>controls; properties of table controls</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>table controls;keyboard-only edit mode</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ; ຄຸນສົມບັດ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຄວບຄຸມ; ຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ; ໂໝດການແກ້ໄຂດ້ວຍຄີບອດເທົ່ານັ້ນ</bookmark_value>"

#. Q4VKE
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3109850\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Special Tips for Table Controls"
msgstr "ເຄັດລັບພິເສດສຳລັບການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ"

#. YN3et
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3153539\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can define a table control to display the records as you like. In other words you can define data fields for displaying or editing data like in a database form."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງເພື່ອສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນຕາມທີ່ຕ້ອງການ."

#. soM75
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3152372\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following fields are possible in a table control: text, date, time and currency field, numeric field, pattern field, check box and combo box. In the case of combined date/time fields, two columns are created automatically."
msgstr "ຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ໃຊ້ໄດ້ໃນຕາຕະລາງໄດ້ແກ່: ຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ວັນທີ, ເວລາ, ສະກຸນເງິນ, ຕົວເລກ, ຮູບແບບ, ຊ່ອງໝາຍ ແລະ ກ່ອງຄອມໂບ."

#. YhmM5
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3159194\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The number of selected lines, if any are selected, is in parentheses after the total number of records."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນແຖວທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ຈະສະແດງໃນວົງເລັບ ຕໍ່ຈາກຈຳນວນຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດ."

#. Qp5F7
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3155616\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To insert columns into the table control, click in the column heads and bring up the context menu. The following commands are available:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອແຊກແຖວ (column) ໃສ່ໃນຕາຕະລາງ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກທີ່ຫົວແຖວແລ້ວເປີດເມນູລັດ."

#. TdSEs
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150789\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Insert Column"
msgstr "ແຊກແຖວ"

#. Exsza
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3153750\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_INSERTCOL\">Calls a submenu to select a data field to adopt it in the table control.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_INSERTCOL\">ເອີ້ນເມນູຍ່ອຍເພື່ອເລືອກຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈະນຳມາໃຊ້ໃນຕາຕະລາງ.</ahelp>"

#. oMrah
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3155552\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Configure the table control using drag and drop: Open the data source browser and drag the desired fields out of the data source browser and on to the column heads of the table control. A pre-configured column is created."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າຕາຕະລາງດ້ວຍການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ: ເປີດຕົວທ່ອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນແລ້ວລາກຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຕ້ອງການມາວາງໃສ່ຫົວແຖວຂອງຕາຕະລາງ."

#. CkFDe
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149827\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Replace with"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນແທນດ້ວຍ"

#. VUawg
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3153345\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_CHANGECOL\">Opens a submenu to select a data field to replace the data field selected in the table control.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_CHANGECOL\">ເປີດເມນູຍ່ອຍເພື່ອເລືອກຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່ທີ່ຈະມາປ່ຽນແທນຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນເດີມ.</ahelp>"

#. zkrru
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3143267\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Delete Column"
msgstr "ລຶບແຖວ"

#. qBe98
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3157958\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_DELETECOL\">Deletes the currently selected column.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_DELETECOL\">ລຶບແຖວທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ.</ahelp>"

#. FKguu
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147275\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Column"
msgstr "ແຖວ"

#. fzvdf
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3152996\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opens the properties dialog of the selected column."
msgstr "ເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງແຖວທີ່ເລືອກ."

#. FQDSR
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148539\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Hide Columns"
msgstr "ເຊື່ອງແຖວ"

#. TAqaE
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3159157\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_HIDECOL\">Hides the selected column.</ahelp> Its properties are not changed."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_HIDECOL\">ເຊື່ອງແຖວທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້.</ahelp> ຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງມັນຈະຍັງຄືເກົ່າ."

#. XbvJf
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150771\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Show columns"
msgstr "ສະແດງແຖວ"

#. 3xqbM
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3159400\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_SHOWCOLS\">Calls a submenu where you can select the columns to show again.</ahelp> To show only one column, click the column name. You see only the first <emph>16</emph> hidden columns. If there are more hidden columns, choose the <emph>More</emph> command to call the <emph>Show Columns</emph> dialog."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_SHOWCOLS\">ເອີ້ນເມນູຍ່ອຍເພື່ອເລືອກແຖວທີ່ຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງອີກຄັ້ງ.</ahelp>"

#. Yc8QE
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3156193\n"
"help.text"
msgid "More"
msgstr "ເພີ່ມເຕີມ"

#. HuXJC
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3159269\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_SHOWCOLS_MORE\">Calls the <emph>Show Columns</emph> dialog.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_SHOWCOLS_MORE\">ເອີ້ນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ສະແດງແຖວ</emph>.</ahelp>"

#. USBtE
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3149763\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/showcoldialog/ShowColDialog\">In the <emph>Show Columns</emph> dialog you can select the columns to be shown. Hold down the <emph>Shift</emph> or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline> key to select multiple entries.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/showcoldialog/ShowColDialog\">ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ສະແດງແຖວ</emph>, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກແຖວທີ່ຈະໃຫ້ສະແດງໄດ້.</ahelp>"

#. KDeGu
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153561\n"
"help.text"
msgid "All"
msgstr "ທັງໝົດ"

#. 9tyR7
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3150504\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_SHOWALLCOLS\">Click <emph>All</emph> if you want to show all columns.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"SID_FM_SHOWALLCOLS\">ຄລິກ <emph>ທັງໝົດ</emph> ຖ້າຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ສະແດງທຸກແຖວ.</ahelp>"

#. 26BCC
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153349\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keyboard-only control of <emph>Table Controls</emph>"
msgstr "ການຄວບຄຸມ <emph>ການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ</emph> ດ້ວຍຄີບອດເທົ່ານັ້ນ"

#. RJx6x
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3149416\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you use the keyboard only to travel through controls in your document, you will find one difference to the other types of controls: the <emph>Tab</emph> key does not move the cursor to the next control, but moves to the next column inside the table control. Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline>+<emph>Tab</emph> to move to the next control, or press <emph>Shift</emph>+<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline>+<emph>Tab</emph> to move to the previous control."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານໃຊ້ຄີບອດເພື່ອເຄື່ອນຍ້າຍ, ປຸ່ມ <emph>Tab</emph> ຈະຍ້າຍໄປຫາແຖວຖັດໄປພາຍໃນຕາຕະລາງ. ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ <emph>Ctrl+Tab</emph> ເພື່ອຍ້າຍໄປຫາການຄວບຄຸມອື່ນ."

#. usstA
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153062\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To enter the special keyboard-only edit mode for <emph>Table Controls</emph>:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອເຂົ້າສູ່ໂໝດການແກ້ໄຂດ້ວຍຄີບອດເທົ່ານັ້ນສຳລັບ <emph>ການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ</emph>:"

#. zyF6P
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3144510\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The form document must be in <link href=\"text/shared/02/01170500.xhp\"><emph>Design mode</emph></link>."
msgstr "ເອກະສານຟອມຕ້ອງຢູ່ໃນ <link href=\"text/shared/02/01170500.xhp\"><emph>ໂໝດອອກແບບ</emph></link>."

#. fzk3Q
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3154758\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline>+<emph>F6</emph> to select the document."
msgstr "ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline>+<emph>F6</emph> ເພື່ອເລືອກເອກະສານ."

#. 8rZYd
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3161657\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <emph>Shift</emph>+<emph>F4</emph> to select the first control. If the <emph>Table Control</emph> is not the first control, press <emph>Tab</emph> until it is selected."
msgstr "ກົດ <emph>Shift+F4</emph> ເພື່ອເລືອກການຄວບຄຸມທຳອິດ."

#. y5xCK
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3151056\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <emph>Enter</emph> to enter the edit mode. The handles are shown farther out from the control border."
msgstr "ກົດ <emph>Enter</emph> ເພື່ອເຂົ້າສູ່ໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ."

#. 2iEME
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3154938\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the edit mode, you can open the edit mode context menu by pressing <emph>Shift</emph>+<emph>F10</emph>."
msgstr "ໃນໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ, ທ່ານສາມາດເປີດເມນູລັດໄດ້ໂດຍການກົດ <emph>Shift+F10</emph>."

#. FGqkC
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3154365\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to edit columns, press <emph>Shift</emph>+<emph>Space</emph> to enter column edit mode. Now you can rearrange the order of columns with <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline>+<emph>Arrow</emph> keys. The <emph>Delete</emph> key deletes the current column."
msgstr "ຖ້າຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂແຖວ, ໃຫ້ກົດ <emph>Shift+Space</emph>. ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດລຽງແຖວໃໝ່ດ້ວຍປຸ່ມ <emph>Ctrl+ລູກສອນ</emph>."

#. Aw4Gz
#: 01170004.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170004.xhp\n"
"par_id3145419\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press the <emph>Esc</emph> key to exit the edit mode."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມ <emph>Esc</emph> ເພື່ອອອກຈາກໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ."

