#. mHJBh
#: 01170102.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170102.xhp\n"
"par_idN11133\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Formula result is copied into the edit field of the combo box."
msgstr "ຜົນລັດຂອງສູດຈະຖືກຄັດລອກໄປໃສ່ຟີວແກ້ໄຂຂອງກ່ອງຄອມໂບ."

#. Vyg5U
#: 01170102.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170102.xhp\n"
"par_idN1113A\n"
"help.text"
