"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>submitting forms</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>get method for form transmissions</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>post method for form transmissions</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການສົ່ງຟອມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ວິທີ Get ສຳລັບການຮັບສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຟອມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ວິທີ Post ສຳລັບການຮັບສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຟອມ</bookmark_value>"

#. XUY8G
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151100\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/02/01170201.xhp\">General</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/02/01170201.xhp\">ທົ່ວໄປ</link>"

#. 68rVo
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3153539\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A form is a text document or spreadsheet with different form controls. If you create a form for a Web page, the user can enter data into it to send over the Internet. The data from the form controls of a form is transmitted to a server by specifying a URL and can be processed on the server."
msgstr "ຟອມຄືເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ສະເປຣດຊີດທີ່ມີການຄວບຄຸມຟອມຕ່າງໆ. ຫາກທ່ານສ້າງຟອມສຳລັບໜ້າເວັບ, ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນລົງໃນນັ້ນເພື່ອສົ່ງຜ່ານອິນເຕີເນັດ. ຂໍ້ມູນຈາກການຄວບຄຸມຟອມຂອງຟອມຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປຍັງເຊີບເວີໂດຍການກຳນົດ URL ແລະ ສາມາດຖືກປະມວນຜົນເທິງເຊີບເວີໄດ້."

#. S6oT3
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149283\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Name"
msgstr "ຊື່"

#. GMJm3
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3150789\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Specifies a name for the form. This name is used to identify the form in the <link href=\"text/shared/02/01170600.xhp\">Form Navigator</link>."
msgstr "ກຳນົດຊື່ສຳລັບຟອມ. ຊື່ນີ້ຖືກໃຊ້ເພື່ອລະບຸຟອມໃນ <link href=\"text/shared/02/01170600.xhp\">ຕົວນຳທາງຟອມ</link>."

#. RStFA
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"hd_id3152425\n"
"help.text"
msgid "URL"
msgstr "URL"

#. 58FDC
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3147226\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Specifies the URL to which the data of the completed form is to be transmitted."
msgstr "ກຳນົດ URL ທີ່ຈະສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຂອງຟອມທີ່ຂຽນສຳເລັດແລ້ວໄປຫາ."

#. PaeRB
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154751\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Frame"
msgstr "ເຟຣມ"

#. J5x3L
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3154823\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Defines the target frame in which the loaded URL is to appear."
msgstr "ກຳນົດເຟຣມປາຍທາງທີ່ URL ທີ່ໂຫຼດຂຶ້ນມາຈະປະກົດໃຫ້ເຫັນ."

#. RETmx
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"hd_id3152551\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Type of submission"
msgstr "ປະເພດການສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. CBWKj
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3155338\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_PROP_SUBMIT_METHOD\">Specifies the method to transfer the completed form information.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_PROP_SUBMIT_METHOD\">ກຳນົດວິທີການໃນການໂອນຍ້າຍຂໍ້ມູນຟອມທີ່ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ.</ahelp>"

#. CwT2d
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3145065\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Using the \"Get\" method, the data of every control is transmitted as an environment variable. They are appended to the URL in the form \"?Control1=Content1&Control2=Content2&...\"; the character string is analyzed by a program on the recipient's server."
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ວິທີ \"Get\", ຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທຸກການຄວບຄຸມຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປເປັນຕົວປ່ຽນສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ (environment variable). ພວກມັນຈະຖືກຕໍ່ທ້າຍ URL ໃນຮູບແບບ \"?Control1=Content1&Control2=Content2&...\"; ຊຸດຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກວິເຄາະໂດຍໂປຣແກຣມໃນເຊີບເວີຂອງຜູ້ຮັບ."

#. E55dQ
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3150443\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Using the \"Post\" method, a document is created from the content of the form that is sent to the specified URL."
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ວິທີ \"Post\", ເອກະສານຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນຈາກເນື້ອໃນຂອງຟອມທີ່ຖືກສົ່ງໄປຍັງ URL ທີ່ກຳນົດ."

#. EhnDZ
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147275\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Submission encoding"
msgstr "ການເຂົ້າລະຫັດການສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. HzL3W
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3159147\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_PROP_SUBMIT_ENCODING\">Specifies the type for encoding the data transfer.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_PROP_SUBMIT_ENCODING\">ກຳນົດປະເພດສຳລັບການເຂົ້າລະຫັດການໂອນຍ້າຍຂໍ້ມູນ.</ahelp>"

#. U9XGk
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155419\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Data transfer of control information"
msgstr "ການໂອນຍ້າຍຂໍ້ມູນຂອງຂໍ້ມູນການຄວບຄຸມ"

#. euwpq
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3153717\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When sending a form, all controls available in $[officename] are taken into consideration. The name of the control and the corresponding value, if available, are transmitted."
msgstr "ເມື່ອສົ່ງຟອມ, ການຄວບຄຸມທັງໝົດທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນ $[officename] ຈະຖືກນຳມາພິຈາລະນາ. ຊື່ຂອງການຄວບຄຸມ ແລະ ຄ່າທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ (ຫາກມີ) ຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປ."

#. kDoEi
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3153252\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Which values are transmitted in each case depends on the respective control. For text fields, the visible entries are transmitted; for list boxes, the selected entries are transmitted; for check boxes and option fields, the associated reference values are transmitted if these fields were activated."
msgstr "ຄ່າໃດທີ່ຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປໃນແຕ່ລະກໍລະນີແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບການຄວບຄຸມນັ້ນໆ. ສຳລັບຟີວຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ລາຍການທີ່ເຫັນໄດ້ຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປ; ສຳລັບກ່ອງລາຍການ, ລາຍການທີ່ຖືກເລືອກຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປ; ສຳລັບກ່ອງໝາຍ ແລະ ຟີວຕົວເລືອກ, ຄ່າອ້າງອີງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປຫາກຟີວເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຖືກເປີດໃຊ້ງານ."

#. MxKP2
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3150984\n"
"help.text"
msgid "How this information is transmitted depends on the selected transfer method (Get or Post) and the coding (URL or Multipart). If the Get method and URL encoding are selected, for example, value pairs in the form <Name>=<Value> are sent."
msgstr "ວິທີການສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບວິທີການໂອນຍ້າຍທີ່ເລືອກ (Get ຫຼື Post) ແລະ ການເຂົ້າລະຫັດ (URL ຫຼື Multipart). ຕົວຢ່າງ ຫາກເລືອກວິທີ Get ແລະ ການເຂົ້າລະຫັດ URL, ຄູ່ຂອງຄ່າໃນຮູບແບບ <Name>=<Value> ຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປ."

#. haYMX
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3157909\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In addition to the controls that are recognized in HTML, $[officename] offers other controls. It should be noted that, for fields with a specific numerical format, the visible values are not transmitted but rather fixed default formats. The following table shows how the data of the $[officename]-specific controls is transmitted:"
msgstr "ນອກເໜືອຈາກການຄວບຄຸມທີ່ຮັບຮູ້ໃນ HTML, $[officename] ຍັງມີການຄວບຄຸມອື່ນໆ ໃຫ້ໃຊ້. ຄວນສັງເກດວ່າ, ສຳລັບຟີວທີ່ມີຮູບແບບຕົວເລກສະເພາະ, ຄ່າທີ່ເຫັນໄດ້ຈະບໍ່ຖືກສົ່ງໄປ ແຕ່ຈະສົ່ງເປັນຮູບແບບເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ແທນ. ຕາຕະລາງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນວິທີການສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຂອງການຄວບຄຸມສະເພາະຂອງ $[officename]:"

#. eDLet
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3153698\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Control"
msgstr "ການຄວບຄຸມ"

#. kZ6JA
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3153562\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Value Pair"
msgstr "ຄູ່ຂອງຄ່າ"

#. QnTLr
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3153823\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Numeric field, currency field"
msgstr "ຟີວຕົວເລກ, ຟີວສະກຸນເງິນ"

#. FWUB9
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3149734\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A decimal separator is always displayed as a period."
msgstr "ຕົວແຍກທົດສະນິຍົມຈະຖືກສະແດງເປັນຈຸດສະເໝີ."

#. vKhpL
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3148563\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Date field"
msgstr "ຟີວວັນທີ"

#. WULKk
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3146794\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The date format is sent in a fixed format (MM-DD-YYYY), regardless of the user's local settings."
msgstr "ຮູບແບບວັນທີຈະຖືກສົ່ງໃນຮູບແບບຄົງທີ່ (MM-DD-YYYY), ໂດຍບໍ່ຄຳນຶງເຖິງການຕັ້ງຄ່າທ້ອງຖິ່ນຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້."

#. T5x27
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3149670\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Time field"
msgstr "ຟີວເວລາ"

#. mrE8G
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3153779\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The time format is sent in a fixed format (HH:MM:SS), regardless of the user's local settings."
msgstr "ຮູບແບບເວລາຈະຖືກສົ່ງໃນຮູບແບບຄົງທີ່ (HH:MM:SS), ໂດຍບໍ່ຄຳນຶງເຖິງການຕັ້ງຄ່າທ້ອງຖິ່ນຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້."

#. RkFrp
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3153361\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Pattern field"
msgstr "ຟີວຮູບແບບ (Pattern field)"

#. D7bBF
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3145419\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The values of pattern fields are sent as text fields, that is, the value visible in the form is sent."
msgstr "ຄ່າຂອງຟີວຮູບແບບຈະຖືກສົ່ງເປັນຟີວຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ນັ້ນຄື ຄ່າທີ່ເຫັນໄດ້ໃນຟອມຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປ."

#. 8GTBK
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3150767\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Table control"
msgstr "ການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ"

#. qsnKF
#: 01170201.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170201.xhp\n"
"par_id3152933\n"
"help.text"
msgid "From the table control, the individual columns are always transmitted. The name of the control, the name of the column, and the value of the column are sent. Using the Get method with URL encoding, the transmission is done in the form <Name of the table control>.<Name of the column>=<Value>, for example, with the value being dependent on the column."
msgstr "ຈາກການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ, ແຕ່ລະຖັນຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປສະເໝີ. ຊື່ຂອງການຄວບຄຸມ, ຊື່ຂອງຖັນ, ແລະ ຄ່າຂອງຖັນຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປ. ການໃຊ້ວິທີ Get ພ້ອມການເຂົ້າລະຫັດ URL, ການສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຈະເຮັດໃນຮູບແບບ <ຊື່ຂອງການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ>.<ຊື່ຂອງຖັນ>=<ຄ່າ>, ຕົວຢ່າງ ເຊັ່ນ ຄ່າທີ່ຂຶ້ນກັບຖັນນັ້ນໆ."

#. GGH2R
