"hd_id3149180\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Value table field"
msgstr "ຟິວຕາຕະລາງຄ່າ"

#. EmQi8
#: 01170903.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170903.xhp\n"
"par_id3150789\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/sabpilot/ui/fieldlinkpage/valuefield\">Specifies the current form data field which should be related to a field in the linked table.</ahelp> In addition, click the desired data field in the list field below."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/sabpilot/ui/fieldlinkpage/valuefield\">ລະບຸຟິວຂໍ້ມູນຂອງຟອມປັດຈຸບັນທີ່ຄວນກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບຟິວໃນຕາຕະລາງທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່.</ahelp> ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ກົດເລືອກຟິວຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຕ້ອງການໃນກ່ອງລາຍການດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#. NREzu
#: 01170903.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01170903.xhp\n"
"par_id3145669\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In <link href=\"text/shared/02/01170102.xhp\">Control - Properties</link>, the specified field will appear as an entry in the <emph>Data</emph> tab page under <emph>Data field</emph>."
msgstr "ໃນ <link href=\"text/shared/02/01170102.xhp\">ຕົວຄວບຄຸມ - ຄຸນສົມບັດ</link>, ຟິວທີ່ລະບຸຈະສະແດງເປັນລາຍການໃນໜ້າແທັບ <emph>ຂໍ້ມູນ</emph> ພາຍໃຕ້ <emph>ຟິວຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>."

#. 9s3QV
