"01171200.xhp\n"
"par_id131686520802424\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enables or disables the grid."
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ ຫຼື ປິດໃຊ້ເສັ້ນຕາໜ່າງ."

#. GwtjF
