"01171300.xhp\n"
"par_idN10589\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Automatically aligns objects to vertical and horizontal grid lines."
msgstr "ຈັດວາງວັດຖຸໃຫ້ກົງກັບເສັ້ນຕາໜ່າງແນວຕັ້ງ ແລະ ແນວນອນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. BUPkp
#: 01171300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01171300.xhp\n"
"par_id321683472243875\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To override this feature, hold down the <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Option</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Alt</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> key when you drag an object."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຍົກເລີກຄຸນສົມບັດນີ້ຊົ່ວຄາວ, ໃຫ້ກົດປຸ່ມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Option</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Alt</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ລາກວັດຖຸ."

