"par_id3148990\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Further information can be found in the Help in <link href=\"text/shared/01/05030500.xhp\"><emph>Borders</emph></link>. You can also find information on how to <link href=\"text/shared/guide/border_table.xhp\"><emph>format a text table</emph></link> with the <emph>Borders</emph> icon."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ໃນສ່ວນຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອໃນ <link href=\"text/shared/01/05030500.xhp\"><emph>ຂອບ</emph></link>. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຊອກຫາຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບວິທີ <link href=\"text/shared/guide/border_table.xhp\"><emph>ຈັດຮູບແບບຕາຕະລາງຂໍ້ຄວາມ</emph></link> ດ້ວຍໄອຄອນ <emph>ຂອບ</emph> ໄດ້."

