"par_id3163829\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Saves the current database table record.</ahelp> The <emph>Save Record</emph> icon is found on the <link href=\"text/shared/main0212.xhp\"><emph>Table Data</emph> bar</link>."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ບັນທຶກລະກອດຕາຕະລາງຖານຂໍ້ມູນປັດຈຸບັນ.</ahelp> ໄອຄອນ <emph>ບັນທຶກລະກອດ</emph> ແມ່ນພົບຢູ່ໃນ <link href=\"text/shared/main0212.xhp\"><emph>ແຖບຂໍ້ມູນຕາຕະລາງ</emph></link>."

#. Yj5gy
#: 07070200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"07070200.xhp\n"
"par_id3152372\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Changes to the contents of a record are automatically saved as soon as you select another record. To save changes without selecting another record, click the <emph>Save Record</emph> icon."
msgstr "ການປ່ຽນແປງເນື້ອໃນຂອງລະກອດຈະຖືກບັນທຶກໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດທັນທີທີ່ທ່ານເລືອກລະກອດອື່ນ. ເພື່ອບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງເລືອກລະກອດອື່ນ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໃສ່ໄອຄອນ <emph>ບັນທຶກລະກອດ</emph>."

