"par_id3144740\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:DSBrowserExplorer\">Turns on and off the view of the data source explorer.</ahelp> The <emph>Explorer On/Off</emph> icon is visible on the <link href=\"text/shared/main0212.xhp\">Table Data bar</link>."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:DSBrowserExplorer\">ເປີດ ແລະ ປິດມຸມມອງຂອງຕົວສຳຫຼວດແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ.</ahelp> ໄອຄອນ <emph>ເປີດ/ປິດ ຕົວສຳຫຼວດ</emph> ຈະສະແດງຢູ່ໃນ <link href=\"text/shared/main0212.xhp\">ແຖບຂໍ້ມູນຕາຕະລາງ</link>."

