#. vPCCe
#: 12070300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12070300.xhp\n"
"par_id3143284\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/insertdbcolumnsdialog/astext\" visibility=\"hidden\">Inserts data selected from the data source browser into the document as text.</ahelp> If you select the <emph>Text</emph> option in the <emph>Insert Database Columns</emph> dialog, the content of the data selected in the data source browser is inserted into the document as text. In the dialog, you can decide which database fields or columns are transferred, and how the text is formatted."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/insertdbcolumnsdialog/astext\" visibility=\"hidden\">ແຊກຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເລືອກຈາກຕົວສຳຫຼວດແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນລົງໃນເອກະສານເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມ.</ahelp> ຫາກທ່ານເລືອກຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ຂໍ້ຄວາມ</emph> ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ແຊກຄໍລໍາຖານຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>, ເນື້ອໃນຂອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເລືອກໃນຕົວສຳຫຼວດແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຈະຖືກແຊກລົງໃນເອກະສານເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ, ທ່ານສາມາດຕັດສິນໃຈໄດ້ວ່າຈະຍ້າຍຟິລ ຫຼື ຄໍລໍາຖານຂໍ້ມູນໃດໄປ, ແລະ ຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກຈັດຮູບແບບແນວໃດ."

#. BGdiC
#: 12070300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12070300.xhp\n"
"par_id3154289\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If several records are selected when you choose the <emph>Data to Text</emph> function, the mail merge fields will be inserted according to the number of records."
msgstr "ຫາກມີຫຼາຍລະບຽນຖືກເລືອກເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກຟັງຊັນ <emph>ຂໍ້ມູນເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມ</emph>, ຟິລຈົດໝາຍວຽນຈະຖືກແຊກຕາມຈຳນວນລະບຽນ."

