"par_id3147226\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>Apply Filter</emph> function retains <link href=\"text/shared/02/12110000.xhp\"><emph>form-based filters</emph></link> that have been set. You do not need to redefine them."
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນ <emph>ນຳໃຊ້ຕົວຕອງ</emph> ຈະຮັກສາ <link href=\"text/shared/02/12110000.xhp\"><emph>ຕົວຕອງຕາມຟອມ</emph></link> ທີ່ໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າໄວ້. ທ່ານບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງກຳນົດພວກມັນໃໝ່."

