"par_id3155535\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the icon again to return to normal mode, in which the changes in the <link href=\"text/sdatabase/02010100.xhp\"><emph>New Query Design</emph></link> are synchronized with the permitted changes through SQL."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ໄອຄອນອີກຄັ້ງເພື່ອ返回ຫາໂໝດປົກກະຕິ, ເຊິ່ງການປ່ຽນແປງໃນ <link href=\"text/sdatabase/02010100.xhp\"><emph>ການອອກແບບການສອບຖາມໃໝ່</emph></link> ຈະຖືກຊິງໂຄຣໄນກັບການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ອະນຸຍາດຜ່ານ SQL."

