#. mED4L
#: 20050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id3147209\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This is the default selection mode for text documents. With the keyboard, selections can be performed by <emph>Shift</emph>+navigation key (<item type=\"keycode\">arrows, Home, End, Page Up, Page Down</item>). With the mouse, click in the text where the selection is to start, hold the left mouse button and move to the end of the selection. Release the mouse key to end selection."
msgstr "ນີ້ແມ່ນໂໝດການເລືອກເລີ່ມຕົ້ນສຳລັບເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ສໍາລັບຄີບອດ, ສາມາດເລືອກໄດ້ໂດຍການກົດ <emph>Shift</emph>+ປຸ່ມນຳທາງ (<item type=\"keycode\">ລູກສອນ, Home, End, Page Up, Page Down</item>). ສຳລັບເມົາສ໌, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໃສ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມບ່ອນທີ່ຕ້ອງການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນການເລືອກ, ກົດປຸ່ມເມົາສ໌ເບື້ອງຊ້າຍຄ້າງໄວ້ ແລ້ວຍ້າຍໄປຫາຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດຂອງການເລືອກ. ປ່ອຍປຸ່ມເມົາສ໌ເພື່ອສິ້ນສຸດການເລືອກ."

#. AZd4x
#: 20050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id3149580\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Extending selection"
msgstr "ການຂະຫຍາຍການເລືອກ"

#. 8V8BG
#: 20050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153717\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the mouse, arrow keys or the <keycode>Home</keycode> and <keycode>End</keycode> keys to extend or crop the current selection. Clicking anywhere in the text selects the region between the current cursor position and the click position."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ເມົາສ໌, ປຸ່ມລູກສອນ ຫຼື ປຸ່ມ <keycode>Home</keycode> ແລະ <keycode>End</keycode> ເພື່ອຂະຫຍາຍ ຫຼື ຕັດການເລືອກປັດຈຸບັນ. ການຄລິກໃສ່ບ່ອນໃດກໍໄດ້ໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະເປັນການເລືອກພື້ນທີ່ລະຫວ່າງຕຳແໜ່ງເຄີເຊີປັດຈຸບັນ ແລະ ຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ຄລິກ."

#. Jwb3c
#: 20050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id821630330412209\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Hold the <keycode>Shift</keycode> key to temporarily activate the Extending selection mode."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມ <keycode>Shift</keycode> ຄ້າງໄວ້ເພື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ໂໝດການຂະຫຍາຍການເລືອກຊົ່ວຄາວ."

#. dL6uZ
#: 20050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id3147620\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Adding selection (<keycode>Shift+F8</keycode>)"
msgstr "ການເພີ່ມການເລືອກ (<keycode>Shift+F8</keycode>)"

#. YjCCD
#: 20050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id3154307\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use this mode to select multiple ranges of text. Each new selection using the mouse or keyboard is added as a new selection."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ໂໝດນີ້ເພື່ອເລືອກຂໍ້ຄວາມຫຼາຍຊ່ວງ. ແຕ່ລະການເລືອກໃໝ່ໂດຍໃຊ້ເມົາສ໌ ຫຼື ຄີບອດຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເປັນການເລືອກໃໝ່."

#. CFmAA
#: 20050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id941630331257314\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Hold the <keycode>Ctrl</keycode> key to temporarily activate the Adding selection mode."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມ <keycode>Ctrl</keycode> ຄ້າງໄວ້ເພື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ໂໝດການເພີ່ມການເລືອກຊົ່ວຄາວ."

#. vSETC
#: 20050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id6971037\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Block selection (<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+F8</keycode>)"
msgstr "ການເລືອກແບບບລັອກ (<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+F8</keycode>)"

#. qAeGQ
#: 20050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id5258644\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use this mode to select a non-contiguous block of text."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ໂໝດນີ້ເພື່ອເລືອກບລັອກຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຕໍ່ເນື່ອງກັນ."

#. tcCu3
