msgctxt ""
"20050000.xhp\n"
"par_id41630331461837\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Hold the <keycode>Alt</keycode> key to temporarily activate the Block selection mode."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມ <keycode>Alt</keycode> ຄ້າງໄວ້ເພື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ໂໝດການເລືອກແບບບລັອກຊົ່ວຄາວ."

