msgstr "ກັບສີ"

#. 2UBh5
#: 24010000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"24010000.xhp\n"
"par_id3145345\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:GraphicFilterInvert\">Inverts the color values of a color image, or the brightness values of a grayscale image. Apply the filter again to revert the effect.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:GraphicFilterInvert\">ກັບຄ່າສີຂອງຮູບພາບສີ ຫຼື ຄ່າຄວາມສະຫວ່າງຂອງຮູບພາບລະດັບສີເທົາ. ນຳໃຊ້ຕົວຕອງອີກຄັ້ງເພື່ອຍົກເລີກຜົນກະທົບ.</ahelp>"

#. 22LEq
