"par_id3150866\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:GraphicFilterRemoveNoise\">Removes noise by applying a median filter.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:GraphicFilterRemoveNoise\">ລຶບສິ່ງລົບກວນອອກໂດຍການນຳໃຊ້ຕົວຕອງແບບ median filter.</ahelp>"

#. cBcLb
