msgctxt ""
"basicshapes.xhp\n"
"par_idN10567\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Opens the Basic Shapes toolbar which you can use to insert graphics into your document.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເປີດແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຮູບຊົງພື້ນຖານ ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອແຊກກຣາຟິກເຂົ້າໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ.</ahelp>"

#. 7ALxL
#: basicshapes.xhp
msgctxt ""
"basicshapes.xhp\n"
"par_idN10591\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Click an icon on the Basic Shapes toolbar, and then drag in the document to draw the shape.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຄລິກທີ່ໄອຄອນເທິງແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຮູບຊົງພື້ນຖານ, ຈາກນັ້ນລາກໃນເອກະສານເພື່ອແຕ້ມຮູບຊົງ.</ahelp>"

#. BDBqG
#: basicshapes.xhp
msgctxt ""
"basicshapes.xhp\n"
"par_idN10594\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some shapes have a handle which you can drag to change the properties of the shape. The mouse pointer changes to a hand symbol over these special handles."
msgstr "ບາງຮູບຊົງມີຈຸດຈັບທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດລາກເພື່ອປ່ຽນຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງຮູບຊົງໄດ້. ຕົວຊີ້ເມົາສ໌ຈະປ່ຽນເປັນສັນຍາລັກຮູບມືເມື່ອຢູ່ເທິງຈຸດຈັບພິເສດເຫຼົ່ານີ້."

